## Estimated Timeline

| Phase                           | Duration                     |
| ------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| Planning & Requirements         | 1 Week                       |
| UI/UX Design                    | 2 Weeks                      |
| Authentication & Profiles       | 2 Weeks                      |
| Discover & Matching             | 3 Weeks                      |
| Messaging & Calls               | 4 Weeks                      |
| Explore & Search                | 2 Weeks                      |
| Payments & Subscriptions        | 2 Weeks                      |
| Verification & Safety           | 2 Weeks                      |
| Admin Panel                     | 3 Weeks                      |
| Testing & QA                    | 3 Weeks                      |
| Google Play Release             | 1 Week                       |
| **Total Estimated Development** | **22–25 Weeks (5–6 Months)** |

This roadmap provides a structured, end-to-end plan from project initiation through launch and post-release growth, aligned with the features and interface shown in your screenshots and using Google Play Billing for subscriptions.